<view class='layout df ais jct' bindtap='close'>
  <view class='main'>
    <view class='main-img df ais'>
      <image 
      wx:for="{{imgList}}"
      wx:for-index="index"
      wx:key="{{index}}"
      mode='widthFix'
      src='{{item}}'>
      </image>
    </view>
    <view class='center'>
      分享多图到微信朋友圈，请先点击
      <text>【保存图片】</text>
      保存图片到您的相册，再点击
      <text>【手动发圈】</text>
      到微信自行选取相应图片分享到您的朋友圈！
    </view>
    <view class='buttom df ais jct-between'>
      <view class='df fdc jct ais'>
        <image src='{{imgUrl + "icon_xiazai@2x (1).png"}}' mode='widthFix'></image>
        <text>保存图片</text>
      </view>
      <view class='df fdc jct ais'>
        <image src='{{imgUrl + "icon_wechat@2x.png"}}' mode='widthFix'></image>
        <text>手动发圈</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>